foreignData.name: Aufgerüttelte Waldwildnis
foreignData.text:
Die Aufgerüttelte Waldwildnis kommt getappt ins Spiel.
{T}: Erhöhe deinen Manavorrat um {G} oder {W}.
{1}{G}{W}: Bis zum Ende des Zuges wird die Aufgerüttelte Waldwildnis zu einer 3/4 grünen und weißen Elementarwesen-Kreatur mit Reichweite. Sie ist immer noch ein Land.

foreignData.name: Fronda agitada
foreignData.text:
La Fronda agitada entra al campo de batalla girada.
{T}: Agrega {G} o {W} a tu reserva de maná.
{1}{G}{W}: Hasta el final del turno, la Fronda agitada es una criatura Elemental verde y blanca 3/4 con la habilidad de alcance. Sigue siendo una tierra.

foreignData.name: Bois sauvage en éveil
foreignData.text:
Le Bois sauvage en éveil arrive sur le champ de bataille engagé.
{T} : Ajoutez {G} ou {W} à votre réserve.
{1}{G}{W} : Jusqu'à la fin du tour, le Bois sauvage en éveil devient une créature 3/4 verte et blanche Élémental avec la portée. C'est toujours un terrain.

foreignData.name: Bosco Selvaggio in Agitazione
foreignData.text:
Il Bosco Selvaggio in Agitazione entra nel campo di battaglia TAPpato.
{T}: Aggiungi {G} o {W} alla tua riserva di mana.
{1}{G}{W}: Fino alla fine del turno, il Bosco Selvaggio in Agitazione diventa una creatura Elementale 3/4 verde e bianca con raggiungere. È ancora una terra.

foreignData.name: 活発な野生林
foreignData.text:
活発な野生林はタップ状態で戦場に出る。
{T}：あなたのマナ・プールに{G}か{W}を加える。
{1}{G}{W}：ターン終了時まで、活発な野生林は到達を持つ緑であり白である３/４のエレメンタル・クリーチャーになる。 それは土地でもある。

foreignData.name: Bosque Selvagem Andarilho
foreignData.text:
Bosque Selvagem Andarilho entra no campo de batalha virado.
{T}: Adicione {G} ou {W} à sua reserva de mana.
{1}{G}{W}: Até o final do turno, Bosque Selvagem Andarilho torna-se uma criatura verde e branca 3/4 do tipo Elemental com alcance. Ela ainda conta como um terreno.

foreignData.name: Беспокойная Чаща
foreignData.text:
Беспокойная Чаща выходит на поле битвы повернутой.
{T}: добавьте {G} или {W} в ваше хранилище маны.
{1}{G}{W}: до конца хода Беспокойная Чаща становится существом 3/4 зеленый и белый Элементаль с Захватом. При этом она остается землей.

foreignData.name: 摇曳丛林
foreignData.text:
摇曳丛林须横置进战场。
{T}：加{G}或{W}到你的法术力池中。
{1}{G}{W}：直到回合结束，摇曳丛林成为3/4绿白双色，具延势异能的元素生物。 它仍然是地。

name: Stirring Wildwood
originalText:
Stirring Wildwood enters the battlefield tapped.
{T}: Add {G} or {W} to your mana pool.
{1}{G}{W}: Until end of turn, Stirring Wildwood becomes a 3/4 green and white Elemental creature with reach. It's still a land.

rulings.text: A land that becomes a creature may be affected by “summoning sickness.” You can’t attack with it or use any of its {T} abilities (including its mana abilities) unless it began your most recent turn on the battlefield under your control. Note that summoning sickness cares about when that permanent came under your control, not when it became a creature.

When a land becomes a creature, that doesn’t count as having a creature enter the battlefield. The permanent was already on the battlefield; it only changed its types. Abilities that trigger whenever a creature enters the battlefield won’t trigger.
